---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About shisaku"
	description="What this devlog is for."
	pubDate={new Date('June 24 2026')}
>
	<p>
		shisaku is a devlog for work in motion: rough notes, prototype write-ups, interface details,
		and the occasional release marker once an idea has earned its place.
	</p>

	<p>
		The name keeps the site pointed at making and trying. Entries can be polished, but they do
		not have to pretend the work arrived fully formed.
	</p>

	<p>
		Expect practical notes, small experiments, and reflections on what changed between first sketch
		and working thing.
	</p>
</Layout>
